Paper: hep-th/0111037

Date: 2001-11-05

Title: Casimir Energy of Confined Fields

Authors: Igor O. Cherednikov

Comments: 5 pages, ijmpa1.sty. Talk at the conference QFEXT01, 10-14 Sep 2001,

Leipzig. Version to be published in IJMPAJournal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A17 (2002) 874-878

A role of the renormalization group invariance in calculations of the groundstate energy for models with confined fermion fields is discussed. The case ofthe (1+1)D MIT bag with massive fermions is studied in detail.